		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (452,1503)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1503,47,'A pale, ordinary man stares out the window at the peak of the Kingsport Head as if longing for something. Pass a <b>Fight (-2) check</b> or discard Lucky Cigarette Case to spark his interest in you and his surroundings. If so, he introduces himself as <b>Thomas Olney</b>. Take his Ally card, or if it''s not available, remove 1 doom token from the Ancient One''s doom track.')");
