		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (431,1440)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1440,42,'\"I guarantee you''ve never seen anything like this!\" Neil holds up a jar containing a small white creature. You may pay $1 to examine it and make a <b>Lore (-1) check</b>. If you pass, gain 2 Clue tokens. If you fail, you gain 1 brood token if Eihort is the Ancient One. Otherwise, nothing happens.')");
