		db.execSQL(sqlInsertCardEnc + " (432,1443)");
		db.execSQL(sqlInsertEnc + " (1443,42,'Neil shows you a grey, warty thing in a jar. As you stare, it slowly opens it eyes and meets your gaze. You may pay $1 to pass a <b>[[Lore check|Lore (-1) [2] check]]</b>. If you pass, you gain 2 Clue tokens and draw 3 Spells, keeping 1 of them. If you don''t pay or fail the check, nothing happens.')");
